{"tid":676651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【佔旺案庭內拍攝】中鐵建：女事主從來不是員工","createTime":"2018-05-24T14:11:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T15:42:30.000Z","uid":39464,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"fa54634af82b27f11f2b4319746139e1afd6fe10","tid":676651,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:11:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180524/s00001/b789044acffb57754393d1a123110bcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180524%2Fs00001%2Fb789044acffb57754393d1a123110bcd.jpg&h=2ed1603c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n周三（23日）佔旺藐視案審訊，一名唐姓內地女子涉嫌在庭上以手機拍攝，根據司法機構周五（24日）審訊案件列表顯示，女事主全名「唐琳玲」(Tang Lin-ling) 。就傳媒報道稱唐女在網上自稱為中鐵建員工， 中鐵建（1186）透過公關回應，「這個人從來不是中鐵建的員工」，對有稱該女子是「投資部副總經理」，中鐵建指「信息也不是真實的」，因沒有此部門及職銜。<br />\n<br />\n根據一位「唐琳玲」（英文名字Aileen Tang）於「京都律師事務所」撰寫《海外併購融資模式案例分析》文章， 個人簡介為悉尼大學金融學碩士，曾任仲量聯行（JLL），中交建（CCCC），中鐵建（CRCC）等。<br />\n<br />\n此外在Linkedin資料中， 一女名曰「Aileen Tang」，亦提及在悉尼大學會計及金融碩士畢業，又提到是中鐵建「Vice President of Investment Dept.」<br />\n<br />\n本港財金界人士之間最近亦流傳一張卡片。一名自稱為「唐琳」女子，自稱中鐵建旗下「中國鐵建國際集團有限公司」投資部副總經理，銜頭除了CPA，並稱為律師，卡片顯示電郵地址上，亦有tanglinling及aileen字眼。<br />\n<br />\n中鐵建（1186）晚上透過公關回應，公司有留意傳媒報道，但唐琳玲或唐琳「從來不是中鐵建國際集團的員工」。對於有稱該女是「投資部副總經理」，中鐵建指此「信息也不是真實的」，澄清該公司並無投資部、更加沒有投資部副經理一職。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180524/s00001/1527167036448\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180524%2Fs00001%2F1527167036448&d=ODzoBClKuUbIDIRA1jo5X%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=0c9fe024\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180524%2Fs00001%2F1527167036448&h=47ca0109\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180524/s00001/1527167036448</a>"},{"pid":"571628f997cb58644a8d490e3f205a0fe8c97f64","tid":676651,"uid":11001,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:12:56.000Z","msg":"支那只有騙子是真的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3357f48fb99f4f5e67bab4892e13a310d05081e","tid":676651,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:17:36.000Z","msg":"光速割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddfc7e894699d97cd7d5aab3e3ff9fe7e92eabd9","tid":676651,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:18:08.000Z","msg":"成個男人咁"},{"pid":"ad77bb424f7f9c9ca2852e3c2652aea6fd2cf810","tid":676651,"uid":21917,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:20:06.000Z","msg":"講割蓆  支那真係快過光速"},{"pid":"151a202aa0bc2f28829dbc55f0d36619cd174d96","tid":676651,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3357f48fb99f4f5e67bab4892e13a310d05081e","tid":676651,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:17:36.000Z","msg":"光速割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd5eb21b45818bf95c9613aff28d7e391b1fe852","tid":676651,"uid":50779,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:22:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c065efe72fe44863b0aed6d2287a014ebe2947c3","tid":676651,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad77bb424f7f9c9ca2852e3c2652aea6fd2cf810","tid":676651,"uid":21917,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:20:06.000Z","msg":"講割蓆  支那真係快過光速"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:22:49.000Z","msg":"棄武將如紙杯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"