<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d9ff2690685e10b25f51c3b6d2da5d96c27166","tid":676651,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:36:06.000Z","msg":"即係共諜嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8765ea175c337f44d4a1fac4ed8c2e5dd5bf2579","tid":676651,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:37:39.000Z","msg":"拉人未？做乜又唔做野？"},{"pid":"1218b41ca284a44af009fec9a64576da66f74e19","tid":676651,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:37:43.000Z","msg":"真心懷疑佢係咪真係澳洲讀書出黎<br />\n如果係而家澳洲留學生質素真係太屎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488b9bacf61ec4379d441ab54fa874b9a36492d1","tid":676651,"uid":48817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:40:04.000Z","msg":"即係唔駛留手啦今次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32f8acdd1534b8bf25902ec4a6e61b91ad9e006","tid":676651,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd98981715d9725a536d253de7a552022628703","tid":676651,"uid":89931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:43:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 畀人割蓆係慘啲嘅"},{"pid":"10d82ab0ad6cf2d69039d324c775c14cfaf0010b","tid":676651,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:47:30.000Z","msg":"只有騙子才是真的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9e86f8481dfdd7bb557619ba058b48671b4d0c","tid":676651,"uid":106247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3357f48fb99f4f5e67bab4892e13a310d05081e","tid":676651,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:17:36.000Z","msg":"光速割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:48:39.000Z","msg":"仲快撚過泛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd14385a2fc259a38012b712a96bf2c64372b9b","tid":676651,"uid":128603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T15:41:31.000Z","msg":"郭美美紅十字會事件<br />\n<br />\n2011年7月1日，中國紅十字會總會發出聲明，宣佈暫停中國商業系統紅十字會一切活動。2012年7月，北京警方對郭美美進行的調查表明郭美美及其母與中國紅十字總會無直接關聯。11月，新上任的中國紅十字會副會長趙白鴿表示「一個都沒有被證實的網絡事件，卻可以用三天就把你打得稀里嘩啦的。」、「三天毀掉一百年。」[9]。中國紅十字會總會在其官方網站發表通報，指明郭美美與中國紅十字會總會及中國商業系統紅十字會沒任何關係，郭美美炫耀的財富與紅十字會、公眾捐款及項目資金沒任何關係。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%83%AD%E7%BE%8E%E7%BE%8E%E7%BA%A2%E5%8D%81%E5%AD%97%E4%BC%9A%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%2583%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E7%25BE%258E%25E7%25BA%25A2%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%25AD%2597%25E4%25BC%259A%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6&d=ODzoBClKuUbIDIRA1jo5X%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=d20e11b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%83%AD%E7%BE%8E%E7%BE%8E%E7%BA%A2%E5%8D%81%E5%AD%97%E4%BC%9A%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6</a>"},{"pid":"0355fe7213791896cd77b3ff6c019562aa208150","tid":676651,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T15:42:22.000Z","msg":"怕咩認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}